Business licenses, saloon licenses...

164
00:20:39,527 --> 00:20:43,839
St. Michael, the archangel,
defend us in battle.

165
00:20:44,007 --> 00:20:47,682
Be our protector against the snares
and the wickedness of the devil.

166
