he hacks up blood on you.

223
00:24:41,647 --> 00:24:44,923
The lime-juicers are nothing but
a bunch of rapacious grab-ups.

224
00:24:45,647 --> 00:24:47,842
The True Blue Americans
say they're a gang...

225
00:24:48,007 --> 00:24:50,646
...but all they do is stand on corners
damning England.

226
00:24:50,807 --> 00:24:53,958
