the British say, you're a fool.

227
00:24:54,127 --> 00:24:57,324
Do any of them got the sand
of the Dead Rabbits?

228
00:25:00,807 --> 00:25:02,877
You don't say that name.

229
00:25:03,047 --> 00:25:07,518
That name died with your...
They been outlawed.

230
