685
01:03:08,367 --> 01:03:10,244
- All right?
- Aye.

686
01:03:12,007 --> 01:03:14,726
So why didn't you dance with Johnny?

687
01:03:16,087 --> 01:03:17,566
Because...

688
01:03:20,047 --> 01:03:22,117
...I didn't want him.

689
01:04:18,007 --> 01:04:20,202
I'm not wanting this.

690
01:04:27,127 --> 01:04:28,116
- Wait.
- What?

691
01:04:28,287 --> 01:04:29,766
Wait.

692
01:04:30,607 --> 01:04:31,756
How does this open?

693
01:04:31,927 --> 01:04:35,761
It takes too long to lace back up.
We'll be here all night.

694
01:04:46,727 --> 01:04:49,525
Sure, all right, I'll take it off.

695
01:05:10,127 --> 01:05:12,846
There was a baby.
They cut it out.

696
01:05:17,047 --> 01:05:18,799
I'm sorry.

697
01:05:19,847 --> 01:05:21,803
Oh, i�s fine.

698
01:05:25,447 --> 01:05:27,802
Have you got any scars?

699
01:05:29,247 --> 01:05:30,965
One or two.

700
01:06:26,767 --> 01:06:28,644
Wha�s that, then?

701
01:06:28,807 --> 01:06:30,126
That?

702
01:06:30,327 --> 01:06:32,636
L�s a gift from Mr. Cutting.

703
01:06:36,807 --> 01:06:38,479
A gift?

